
### 2. Edge 扩展文件
#### `solution-a-auto-sitelist/edge-extension/manifest.json`
```json
{
  "manifest_version": 3,
  "name": "IE 模式一键打开",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "点击图标自动将当前站点加入IE模式白名单并打开",
  "permissions": ["nativeMessaging", "tabs"],
  "action": {
    "default_title": "IE模式打开当前页面",
    "default_icon": {
      "16": "icons/icon.png",
      "48": "icons/icon.png",
      "128": "icons/icon.png"
    }
  },
  "icons": {
    "16": "icons/icon.png",
    "48": "icons/icon.png",
    "128": "icons/icon.png"
  },
  "background": {
    "service_worker": "background.js"
  }
}